      • terSinistro

        public void terSinistro()
        Method responsible for set if the vehicle had a car accident or not. if the car already had a car accident it will decrease the client insurance bonus. This method also returns a message saying the model of the vehicle, the name of the client, if the client had or not a car accident and how much is the currently bonus.
        Specified by:
        terSinistro in interface IAlteraSeguro

      • calcularBonus

        public void calcularBonus()
        Method responsible for calculate the bonus based if the client already had a car accident or not. if the client already had a car accident it will decrease the bonus -1, if not it will increase +1.
        Specified by:
        calcularBonus in interface IAlteraSeguro
